gnore\")\n\n[.pre-commit-config.yaml](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/.pre-commit-config.yaml \".pre-commit-config.yaml\")\n\n[.pre-commit-config.yaml](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/.pre-commit-config.yaml \".pre-commit-config.yaml\")\n\n[README.md](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/README.md \"README.md\")\n\n[README.md](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/README.md \"README.md\")\n\n[commitlint.config.js](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/commitlint.config.js \"commitlint.config.js\")\n\n[commitlint.config.js](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/commitlint.config.js \"commitlint.config.js\")\n\n[license.txt](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/license.txt \"license.txt\")\n\n[license.txt](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/license.txt \"license.txt\")\n\n[pyproject.toml](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/pyproject.toml \"pyproject.toml\")\n\n[pyproject.toml](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/pyproject.toml \"pyproject.toml\")\n\nView all files\n\n## Repository files navigation\n\n-   [README](#)\n-   [MIT license](#)\n\n# Payments\n\n[](#payments)\n\nA payments app for frappe.\n\n## Installation\n\n[](#installation)\n\n1.  Install [bench & frappe](https://frappeframework.com/docs/v14/user/en/installation).\n    \n2.  Once setup is complete, add the payments app to your bench by running\n    \n    ```\n    $ bench get-app payments\n    ```\n    \n3.  Install the payments app on the required site by running\n    \n    ```\n    $ bench --site <sitename> install-app payments\n    ```\n    \n\n## App Structure & Details\n\n[](#app-structure--details)\n\nApp has 2 modules - Payments and Payment Gateways.\n\nPayment Module contains the Payment Gateway DocType which creates links for the payment gateways and Payment Gateways Module contain all the Payment Gateway (Razorpay, Stripe, Braintree, Paypal, PayTM) DocTypes.\n\nApp adds custom fields to Web Form for facilitating payments upon installation and removes them upon uninstallation.\n\nAll general utils are stored in [utils](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/payments/utils) directory. The utils are written in [utils.py](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/payments/utils/utils.py) and then imported into the [`__init__.py`](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/payments/utils/__init__.py) file for easier importing/namespacing.\n\n[overrides](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/payments/overrides) directory has all the overrides for overriding standard frappe code. Currently it overrides WebForm DocType controller as well as a WebForm whitelisted method.\n\n[templates](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/payments/templates) directory has all the payment gateways' custom checkout pages.\n\n## Ongoing Work\n\n[](#ongoing-work)\n\n-   New API design: [#53](https://github.com/frappe/payments/pull/53)\n-   Mollie Integration: [#68](https://github.com/frappe/payments/pull/68) (awaiting the former, but you may use the branc)\n\n## License\n\n[](#license)\n\nMIT ([license.txt](/frappe/payments/blob/develop/license.txt))\n\n## About\n\nA payments app for frappe\n\n### Resources\n\n[Readme](#readme-ov-file)\n\n### License\n\n[MIT license](#MIT-1-ov-file)\n\n### Uh oh!\n\nThere was an error while loading. Please reload this page.\n\n[Activity](/frappe/payments/activity)\n\n[Custom properties](/frappe/payments/custom-properties)\n\n### Stars\n\n[**168** stars](/frappe/payments/stargazers)\n\n### Watchers\n\n[**17** watching](/frappe/payments/watchers)\n\n### Forks\n\n[**401** forks](/frappe/payments/forks)\n\n[Report repository](/contact/report-content?content_url=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Ffrappe%2Fpayments&report=frappe+%28user%29)\n\n## [Releases](/frappe/payments/releases)\n\nNo releases published\n\n## [Packages 0](/orgs/frappe/packages?repo_name=payments)\n\n### Uh oh!\n\nThere was an error while loading. Please reload this page.\n\n### Uh oh!\n\nThere was an error while loading. Please reload this page.\n\n## [Contributors](/frappe/payments/graphs/contributors)\n\n### Uh oh!\n\nThere was an error while loading. Please reload this page.\n\n## Languages\n\n-  