hread` | Check | No | read_only |\n| `is_self_message` | Check | No | set_only_once |\n| `is_archived` | Check | No | |\n| `last_message_timestamp` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `dm_user_1` | Link→Raven User | No | read_only |\n| `dm_user_2` | Link→Raven User | No | read_only |\n| `last_message_details` | JSON | No | read_only |\n| `pinned_messages` | Table | No | Options: \"Raven Pinned Messages\" |\n| `pinned_messages_string` | Small Text | No | |\n| `is_ai_thread` | Check | No | read_only |\n| `openai_thread_id` | Data | No | read_only |\n| `thread_bot` | Link→Raven Bot | No | read_only |\n\n### Raven Message\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `channel_id` | Link→Raven Channel | Yes | search_index |\n| `text` | Long Text | No | |\n| `json` | JSON | No | |\n| `message_reactions` | JSON | No | |\n| `is_reply` | Check | No | |\n| `linked_message` | Link→Raven Message | No | |\n| `replied_message_details` | JSON | No | |\n| `links` | Small Text | No | |\n| `is_thread` | Check | No | |\n| `message_type` | Select | No | Options: Text, Image, File, Poll, System |\n| `content` | Long Text | No | read_only |\n| `file` | Attach | No | |\n| `image_width` | Data | No | |\n| `image_height` | Data | No | |\n| `blurhash` | Small Text | No | |\n| `file_thumbnail` | Attach | No | |\n| `thumbnail_width` | Data | No | |\n| `thumbnail_height` | Data | No | |\n| `link_doctype` | Link→DocType | No | |\n| `link_document` | Dynamic Link | No | search_index |\n| `is_edited` | Check | No | |\n| `is_forwarded` | Check | No | |\n| `mentions` | Table | No | Options: \"Raven Mention\" |\n| `poll_id` | Link→Raven Poll | No | unique |\n| `is_bot_message` | Check | No | |\n| `bot` | Link→Raven User | No | mandatory_depends_on |\n| `hide_link_preview` | Check | No | |\n| `notification` | Data | No | read_only |\n\n---\n\n## 4. Helpdesk (Support/Ticketing)\n\n### HD Ticket\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `subject` | Data | Yes | in_global_search, in_standard_filter |\n| `raised_by` | Data (Email) | No | in_global_search |\n| `status` | Link→HD Ticket Status | No | search_index |\n| `priority` | Link→HD Ticket Priority | No | |\n| `status_category` | Data | No | fetch_from: status.category, read_only |\n| `ticket_type` | Link→HD Ticket Type | No | |\n| `agent_group` | Link→HD Team | No | |\n| `summary` | Text Editor | No | |\n| `description` | Text Editor | No | in_global_search |\n| `template` | Link→HD Ticket Template | No | |\n| `key` | Data | No | read_only, set_only_once |\n| `sla` | Link→HD Service Level Agreement | No | |\n| `response_by` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `raised_outside_working_hours` | Check | No | read_only |\n| `agreement_status` | Select | No | Options: First Response Due, Resolution Due, Failed, Fulfilled, Paused |\n| `resolution_by` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `service_level_agreement_creation` | Datetime | No | hidden, read_only |\n| `on_hold_since` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `total_hold_time` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `first_response_time` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `first_responded_on` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `first_response_failed_by` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `avg_response_time` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `last_agent_response` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `last_customer_response` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `resolution_details` | Text Editor | No | no_copy |\n| `opening_date` | Date | No | read_only |\n| `opening_time` | Time | No | read_only |\n| `resolution_date` | Datetime | No | read_only |\n| `resolution_time` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `user_resolution_time` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `resolution_failed_by` | Duration | No | read_only |\n| `contact` | Link→Contact | No | timeline_field |\n| `customer` | Link→HD Customer | No | |\n| `email_account` | Link→Email Account | No | |\n| `via_customer_portal` | Check | No | |\n| `attachment` | Attach | No | hidden |\n| `content_type` | Data | No | hidden |\n| `is_merged` | Check | No | read_only |\n| `merged_with` | Link→HD Ticket | No | read_only |\n| `ticket_split_from` | Link→HD Ticket | No | read_only |\n| `feedback_rating` | Rating | No | read_only |\n| `feedback` | Link→HD Ticket Feedback Option | No | read_only |\n| `feedback_extra` | Long Text | No | read_only |\n\n---\n\n## 5. EPS (Energy Points System)\n\n### Energy Point Log\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `user` | Link→User | Yes | read_only, search_index |\n| `type` | Select | No | Options: Auto, Appreciation, Criticism, Review, Revert |\n| `points` | Int | No | read_only |\n| `rule` | Link→Energy Point Rule | No | read_only |\n| `reference_doctype` | Link→DocType | No | read_only |\n| `reference_name` | Data | No | read_only |\n| `reverted` | Check | No | hidden |\n| `revert_of` | Link→Energy Point Log | No | read_only |\n| `reason` | Text | No | read_only |\n| `seen` | Check | No | hidden |\n\n### Energy Point Rule\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `enabled` | Check | Yes | Default: 1 |\n| `rule_name` | Data | Yes | unique |\n| `reference_doctype` | Link→DocType | Yes | |\n| `for_doc_event` | Select | No | Options: New, Submit, Cancel, Value Change, Custom |\n| `field_to_check` | Select | No | depends_on: Value Change |\n| `points` | Int | Yes | |\n| `for_assigned_users` | Check | No | |\n| `user_field` | Select | No | |\n| `multiplier_field` | Select | No | |\n| `max_points` | Int | No | |\n| `apply_only_once` | Check | No | |\n| `condition` | Code | No | |\n\n### Energy Point Settings (Singleton)\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `enabled` | Check | No | |\n| `review_levels` | Table | No | Options: \"Review Level\" |\n| `point_allocation_periodicity` | Select | No | Options: Daily, Weekly, Monthly |\n| `last_point_allocation_date` | Date | No | read_only |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Payments (Payment/Subscription)\n\n### Payment Gateway\n| Field | Fieldtype | Required | Notes |\n|-------|-----------|----------|-------|\n| `gateway` | Data | Yes | unique, autoname |\n| `gateway_settings` | Link→DocType | No | |\n| `gateway_controller` | Dynamic Link | No | Options: gateway_settings |\n\n---\n\n## Key Relationships Map\n\n```\nGameplan:\n  GP Team ──< GP Project (team)\n  GP Project ──< GP Discussion (project)\n  GP Discussion ──< GP Comment (reference_doctype)\n  GP Discussion ──< GP Reaction (reactions table)\n  GP Comment ──< GP Reaction (reactions table)\n  User ──── GP User Profile (user)\n\nLMS:\n  LMS Course ──< Course Chapter ──< Course Lesson\n  LMS Course ──< LMS Enrollment\n  LMS Batch ──< LMS Batch Enrollment\n  LMS Course ──< LMS Course Progress\n  LMS Course ──< LMS Certificate\n\nRaven:\n  Raven Channel ──< Raven Channel Member\n  Raven Channel ──< Raven Message (channel_id)\n  Raven Message ──< Raven Mention (mentions table)\n\nHelpdesk:\n  HD Ticket ──< HD Ticket Comment\n  HD Team ──< HD Agent\n  HD Service Level Agreement ──< HD Ticket\n\nEPS:\n  Energy Point Rule ──> Energy Point Log\n  User ──── Energy Point Log (user)\n```\n\n## Frappe Field Types Reference\n- **Data**: Text field\n- **Text Editor**: Rich text (HTML)\n- **Small Text**: Multi-line text\n- **Long Text**: Large text block\n- **Link**: Foreign key (options = target DocType)\n- **Dynamic Link**: FK where target is specified by another field\n- **Table**: Child table (options = child DocType)\n- **Table MultiSelect**: Multi-select from child table\n- **Check**: Boolean (0/1)\n- **Select**: Dropdown (options = newline-separated)\n- **Attach/Attach Image**: File upload\n- **Date/Datetime/Time**: Date/time fields\n- **Int/Float/Currency**: Numeric\n- **JSON**: JSON data storage\n- **Code**: Code editor (options = language)\n- **Color**: Color picker\n- **Rating**: Star rating",
      "timestamp": 1781948604202
